# Data Sources

This document summarizes the primary data sources, public reports, financial disclosures, investor materials, press releases, and archived references used in the Global Mega-Studios / Super-Indies Financial Dashboard.

本ファイルは、Global Mega-Studios / Super-Indies Financial Dashboard で使用している財務データ、企業開示資料、IR資料、M&A関連情報、調査レポート、アーカイブリンク等を整理するための出典管理ファイルです。

## Dashboard Scope

- Revenue trends of major global and European production studio groups
- EBITA / EBITDA margin trends
- Business model mix by production, distribution, streaming, licensing, and related activities
- M&A-driven growth and ownership changes
- Comparative analysis of major Super-Indies and mega-studio groups from 2015 to 2025

## Covered Companies

The dashboard focuses on the following production studio groups:

- Banijay
- Fremantle
- ITV Studios
- BBC Studios
- Mediawan
- All3Media

